"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1932686-olympics-2024-star-trolls-old-opponents-Christopher-Morales-Williams\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Olympian Christopher Morales-Williams hit back at his 'old' competitors ahead of the 400 metre semi-final later today.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 120, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Morales-Williams, who turned 20 earlier this week, booked his spot in the semi-final with a stellar run during Sunday's heat.\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 247, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Canadian finished second in his qualification run, completing one lap of the athletics track in just under 45 seconds.\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 253, \"end\": 261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.8990549475220034, \"rank\": 0.11226221933216049, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, when quizzed on his performance, Morales-Williams revealed competing at the Olympics wasn't even the hardest thing he'd ever done.\", \"from\": 373, \"to\": 512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking after the event, the 400m runner said: \\\"I was talking with Coach Caryl [Smith-Gilbert], she was telling me 'You have done harder things than this already.'\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SECs [the US college championship] was harder.\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 689, \"end\": 691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.971006185845272, \"rank\": 0.02964072405141772, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"SECs last year was harder than any race I have done this year.\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The hardest part was just getting to be that fast.\\\"\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Morales-Williams is right to reference the SECs, given he recorded the fastest 400-metre time in the world this year at the event earlier this year.\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The University of Georgia runner went at 44.05 seconds - a time that could see him challenge for a medal in Paris.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1102, \"end\": 1107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999542410488, \"rank\": 4.575900905825605e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile...one of the funniest interviews of the Olympics so far was when NCAA champion Christopher Morales-Williams of@UGATrackwas asked about handling pressure at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1185, \"end\": 1198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NCAA_Men's_Outdoor_Track_and_Field_Championship\", \"score\": 0.9999981201844481, \"rank\": 1.8798190137176478e-06, \"text\": \"NCAA champion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NCAA_Men's_Outdoor_Track_and_Field_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NCAA_Men's_Outdoor_Track_and_Field_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's 19 years old and representing Canada and just advanced to the semifinal.Here's what he\\u2026pic.twitter.com/jbFxznPfS9    But when speaking about what he plans to do if the semi-final does not go his way, Morales-Williams added: \\\"Now I just go out there and have fun.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1325, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9734249157822997, \"rank\": 0.02725867607442682, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I lose, I just go back to school and continue on with my life.\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But these guys, you know, they are old.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They have got cars, and kids.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1695, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not even own a car, I do not even have to pay for gas.\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So it's like, what do I even need to worry about?\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Spending money on pencils?\\\"\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the coy approach, Morales-Williams will be hoping to impress when he returns to the track for the 400-metre semis.\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:'Genius' reason Olympians wear all black clothes when competing  Do not miss:Luana Alonso breaks her silence after claims she was 'inappropriate' at Olympics  Do not miss:Gabby Logan issues sad health update after suffering 'brain fog' at Olympics  He's been placed in a semi-final with Michael Norman, who placed fifth in the 400 metres at the last Games.\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2050, \"end\": 2055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\", \"score\": 0.8124999943799553, \"rank\": 0.23076923076919917, \"text\": \"Luana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\"}, {\"begin\": 2260, \"end\": 2274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mick_Norman\", \"score\": 0.9938258882926672, \"rank\": 0.006100909081937267, \"text\": \"Michael Norman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mick_Norman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mick_Norman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The British and European record holder Matthew Hudson-Smith will also take to the blocks in Morales-Williams' heat.\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2335, \"end\": 2342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9906832427165326, \"rank\": 0.005439563772267349, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2347, \"end\": 2362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 9.774089081961003e-12, \"text\": \"European record\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\"}, {\"begin\": 2370, \"end\": 2390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hudson-Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matthew Hudson-Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hudson-Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hudson-Smith\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hudson-Smith boasts a personal best of 43.74, which he recorded at the London Diamon League meeting last month.\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2519, \"end\": 2525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999995835351868, \"rank\": 3.8257590679260224e-07, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\